rows.label: tlk41100141_04_msg0001
rows.name: Hey, I just had a great idea!

rows.label: tlk41100141_04_msg0002
rows.name:
A way to stop everyone from fighting,
so there won't be any more war
orphans like me!

rows.label: tlk41100141_04_msg0003
rows.name:
It's easy - we just have to not get
involved with the other Divine Beasts at all!

rows.label: tlk41100141_04_msg0004
rows.name:
In Invidia's case, we should just never
leave the inside of the Divine Beast.

rows.label: tlk41100141_04_msg0005
rows.name:
If we cut contact from other countries,
there won't be any more fighting, right?

rows.label: tlk41100141_04_msg0007
rows.name:
There's a country that tried that
already?!

rows.label: tlk41100141_04_msg0009
rows.name:
Yeah...I guess a Bunnit-brained idea
like that was never going to work...
